---
title: Easy Sesame Tofu with Veggie-Tossed Rice
description: Sesame-crusted tofu, tossed in honey garlic sauce and served with veggie-studded rice, is the perfect dinner for even the pickiest eaters!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tofu-au-sesame-684978e4.jpg
